channel.title: Respawn
channel.description: Hey guys, whenever you die in the Duel Arena on my server, it respawns you at a certain location and I want to change those coords, what folder do I do that in?

item.title: Respawn
item.dc:creator: @Skiire Skiire
item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

What RandQm is saying is find out which coords it is using then.

If it’s not using your Duel_Respawn_X, find out which one it is using. Then find out where it’s being called, change it to Duel_Respawn_X there.
